PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1991-1680 (which fixed the rates of remuneration payable to the members of the ROYAL COMMISSION ON ABORIGINAL PEOPLES) so as to provide for the reimbursement of actual and reasonable travelling expenses incurred by the Commissioners while travelling in remote areas of northern Canada.
